"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1933919-Team-GB-Olympics-Jade-Jones-drugs-test\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  DoubleOlympicchampion Jade Jones has vehemently denied allegations of drug use after her attempt to make taekwondo history in Paris was cut short in the first round.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 128, \"end\": 133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998830903747, \"rank\": 1.1690972813246609e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am obviously not on drugs, I just lost,\\\" the Flint fighter declared.\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 217, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.658684881926614e-16, \"text\": \"Flint\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flint\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jones, 31, avoided punishment from the UK Anti-Doping Agency (UKAD) for a doping violation in December last year when she failed to provide a urine sample.\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 280, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Anti-Doping\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\"}, {\"begin\": 280, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Anti-Doping\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"UKAD referred to \\\"very exceptional circumstances\\\" linked to confidential medical records and stated there was \\\"no fault or negligence for her refusal\\\".\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Welsh athlete had signed a document stating she was unable to provide a sample due to dehydration training before a weigh-in, which involved not eating or drinking.\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Later that day, she provided a sample which tested negative.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 780, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She had been provisionally suspended before being cleared.\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking publicly about the incident for the first time, Jones asserted: \\\"I can confirm that I have never taken drugs.\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 960, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have done hundreds of tests and since then I have done 13 more tests - more than ever.\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am obviously not on drugs, I just lost.\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very grateful to people for looking into it properly.\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1154, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I made a mistake.\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They came on dehydration day, I wasn't in the right mind.\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are losing weight and you have not eaten or drank for a few days.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I needed to dehydrate.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I become stressed.\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought you could miss three.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I signed a piece of paper but I did not know what I was signing.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was lucky they looked into it and it all got sorted and it got proven I was innocent.\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just so grateful, blessed that they looked into it, that I was cleared, I was in no fault.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1627, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a big story.\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't one thing..I was grateful to be here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1696, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jones, who won gold in London 2012 at the age of 19 and successfully defended her title in Rio, had been aiming to make history as the first three-time Olympic champion in her sport.\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1721, \"end\": 1732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999567926361, \"rank\": 4.320726528702484e-08, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1789, \"end\": 1792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7788586433324891, \"rank\": 0.28393002827175284, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she suffered a first-round defeat in the -57kg category to Miljana Reljikj after the match ended in a draw and the Macedonian advanced on a tiebreaker based on the number of registered hits.\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 2081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2006, \"end\": 2016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macedonian_language\", \"score\": 0.8346340771147164, \"rank\": 0.09631084907554893, \"text\": \"Macedonian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macedonian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macedonian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on her loss, Jones, who is now contemplating retirement, expressed: \\\"I am devastated.\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I came here to win, I thought I could win, and on the day I did not have the balls that it took and that made the difference.\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"It was the expectation, the pressure, obviously I was trying to do something no one had done.\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew I could be good enough and then when it comes down to it sometimes you just freeze, you want it too much almost.\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just wasn't letting my legs go, wasn't listening to my coach, not in the zone.\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Was I in shape?\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2866, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, physically but obviously not mentally.\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It (the drug test issue) did not help but that's not reason why I lost.\\\"\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3123, \"end\": 3136, \"title\